snippet.textDisplay: The original video was made with UFO glue, some people replicated it with UHU. UFO is actually Cyanoacrylate, UHU is a resin composite. Superglue instantly cures with this water and forms a hard surface, UHU forms a rubber. (UFO is a cheap rip off from China)
